"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(DISTINCT molecule.molecule_id)\nFROM molecule\nJOIN bond ON molecule.molecule_id = bond.molecule_id\nWHERE molecule.label = '-' AND bond.bond_type = '-';\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the number of distinct molecules that have at least one single bond and are non-carcinogenic. It joins the `molecule` and `bond` tables on the `molecule_id` and applies the conditions specified in the evidence."